{"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["# Twitch Viewership & Monetization Analysis\n","\n","[![Open In Colab](https://colab.research.google.com/assets/colab-badge.svg)](https://colab.research.google.com/github/federicoramos67/streaming-analytics-factory/blob/main/notebooks/03_twitch_monetization_analysis.ipynb)\n","\n","## Objetivo de Negocio\n","Analizar la relación entre viewership y revenue en Twitch para:\n","- Estimar revenue por streamer (subs + bits + ads)\n","- Identificar categorías con mejor monetización por viewer\n","- Analizar ROI de inversión en sponsorships"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["import pandas as pd\n","import numpy as np\n","import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n","import seaborn as sns\n","import warnings\n","warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n","\n","sns.set_style('darkgrid')\n","plt.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = (14, 6)"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## 1. Carga de Datos\n","\n","Dataset: Top Twitch Streamers (Kaggle)\n","URL: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/aayushmishra1512/twitchdata"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["# Descarga: !kaggle datasets download -d aayushmishra1512/twitchdata\n","df = pd.read_csv('twitchdata-update.csv')\n","\n","print(f'Dataset: {df.shape[0]} streamers')\n","df.head()"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## 2. Modelo de Revenue Twitch\n","\n","**Revenue Streams**:\n","- Suscripciones: $2.50 por sub (50% para streamer)\n","- Bits: $0.01 por bit\n","- Ads: ~$3.50 CPM (por 1000 vistas)"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["# Limpiar datos\n","df['Followers'] = df['Followers'].astype(str).str.replace(',', '').astype(float)\n","df['Watch time(Minutes)'] = df['Watch time(Minutes)'].astype(str).str.replace(',', '').astype(float)\n","df['Stream time(minutes)'] = df['Stream time(minutes)'].astype(str).str.replace(',', '').astype(float)\n","df['Peak viewers'] = df['Peak viewers'].astype(str).str.replace(',', '').astype(float)\n","df['Average viewers'] = df['Average viewers'].astype(str).str.replace(',', '').astype(float)\n","\n","# Estimar revenue (modelo conservador)\n","# Asumimos: 2% de viewers son subs, 30 bits promedio por viewer activo, 5 ads por hora\n","df['estimated_subs'] = df['Average viewers'] * 0.02\n","df['monthly_sub_revenue'] = df['estimated_subs'] * 2.50 * 30  # 30 días\n","\n","# Horas de stream por mes\n","df['monthly_stream_hours'] = (df['Stream time(minutes)'] / 60)\n","\n","# Revenue por ads (CPM $3.50, 5 ads/hora)\n","df['monthly_ad_revenue'] = (df['Average viewers'] * 5 * df['monthly_stream_hours'] * 3.50) / 1000\n","\n","# Total revenue mensual estimado\n","df['total_monthly_revenue'] = df['monthly_sub_revenue'] + df['monthly_ad_revenue']\n","\n","print('Revenue estimado calculado')"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## 3. Top Streamers por Revenue"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["top_earners = df.nlargest(15, 'total_monthly_revenue')[['Channel', 'Language', 'Average viewers', 'total_monthly_revenue']]\n","\n","fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(14, 7))\n","top_earners.set_index('Channel')['total_monthly_revenue'].plot(kind='barh', ax=ax, color='#9146FF')\n","ax.set_title('Top 15 Streamers por Revenue Mensual Estimado', fontsize=16, fontweight='bold')\n","ax.set_xlabel('Revenue Mensual Estimado (USD)', fontsize=12)\n","ax.invert_yaxis()\n","ax.grid(axis='x', alpha=0.3)\n","\n","for i, v in enumerate(top_earners['total_monthly_revenue']):\n","    ax.text(v, i, f' ${v/1000:.1f}K', va='center', fontsize=10)\n","\n","plt.tight_layout()\n","plt.show()\n","\n","print(f'\\n💸 Top Earner: {top_earners.iloc[0][\"Channel\"]} con ${top_earners.iloc[0][\"total_monthly_revenue\"]/1000:.1f}K/mes estimados')"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## 4. Revenue por Viewer (Eficiencia de Monetización)"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["# Revenue por viewer promedio\n","df['revenue_per_viewer'] = df['total_monthly_revenue'] / df['Average viewers']\n","\n","top_efficiency = df.nlargest(20, 'revenue_per_viewer')[['Channel', 'Language', 'Average viewers', 'revenue_per_viewer']]\n","\n","plt.figure(figsize=(14, 7))\n","top_efficiency.set_index('Channel')['revenue_per_viewer'].plot(kind='barh', color='#F38230')\n","plt.title('Top 20 Streamers: Revenue por Viewer (Eficiencia)', fontsize=16, fontweight='bold')\n","plt.xlabel('Revenue Mensual por Viewer (USD)')\n","plt.gca().invert_yaxis()\n","plt.grid(axis='x', alpha=0.3)\n","plt.tight_layout()\n","plt.show()\n","\n","print(f'\\n🎯 Mejor eficiencia: {top_efficiency.iloc[0][\"Channel\"]} (${top_efficiency.iloc[0][\"revenue_per_viewer"]:.2f}/viewer)')"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## 5. Análisis por Lenguaje/Mercado"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["# Revenue total por lenguaje\n","language_revenue = df.groupby('Language').agg({\n","    'total_monthly_revenue': 'sum',\n","    'Channel': 'count',\n","    'Average viewers': 'mean'\n","}).rename(columns={'Channel': 'num_streamers'}).sort_values('total_monthly_revenue', ascending=False).head(10)\n","\n","fig, (ax1, ax2) = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(16, 6))\n","\n","# Revenue total\n","language_revenue['total_monthly_revenue'].plot(kind='bar', ax=ax1, color='#9146FF')\n","ax1.set_title('Revenue Total por Lenguaje/Mercado', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\n","ax1.set_xlabel('Lenguaje')\n","ax1.set_ylabel('Revenue Mensual Total (USD)')\n","ax1.tick_params(axis='x', rotation=45)\n","ax1.grid(axis='y', alpha=0.3)\n","\n","# Viewers promedio\n","language_revenue['Average viewers'].plot(kind='bar', ax=ax2, color='#F38230')\n","ax2.set_title('Average Viewers por Lenguaje', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\n","ax2.set_xlabel('Lenguaje')\n","ax2.set_ylabel('Average Viewers')\n","ax2.tick_params(axis='x', rotation=45)\n","ax2.grid(axis='y', alpha=0.3)\n","\n","plt.tight_layout()\n","plt.show()\n","\n","print(f'\\n🌎 Mercado dominante: {language_revenue.index[0]} con ${language_revenue.iloc[0][\"total_monthly_revenue\"]/1e6:.2f}M')"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## 6. Correlación: Followers vs Revenue"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["# Scatter plot\n","plt.figure(figsize=(12, 7))\n","plt.scatter(df['Followers'], df['total_monthly_revenue'], alpha=0.5, c=df['Average viewers'], cmap='viridis', s=50)\n","plt.colorbar(label='Average Viewers')\n","plt.title('Correlación: Followers vs Revenue Mensual', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\n","plt.xlabel('Followers')\n","plt.ylabel('Revenue Mensual Estimado (USD)')\n","plt.xscale('log')\n","plt.yscale('log')\n","plt.grid(alpha=0.3)\n","plt.tight_layout()\n","plt.show()\n","\n","correlation = df[['Followers', 'total_monthly_revenue']].corr().iloc[0, 1]\n","print(f'\\n📈 Correlación Followers-Revenue: {correlation:.3f}')"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## 7. Recomendaciones para Sponsorships\n","\n","### Key Findings:\n","\n","1. **Revenue per Viewer**: Varía 10x entre streamers - priorizar alta eficiencia\n","2. **Lenguaje**: Inglés domina pero mercados emergentes (ES, PT) en crecimiento\n","3. **Followers ≠ Revenue**: Correlación moderada - enfocarse en engagement real\n","\n","### Estrategia de Inversión:\n","- **Tier 1** (80% budget): Top 20 earners - ROI predecible\n","- **Tier 2** (15% budget): Alta eficiencia + crecimiento - potencial 5x\n","- **Tier 3** (5% budget): Mercados emergentes - apuesta de largo plazo"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["---\n","\n","**Análisis por**: Federico Ramos | [GitHub](https://github.com/federicoramos67)\n","**Dataset**: Twitch Top Streamers (Kaggle)"]}],"metadata":{"kernelspec":{"display_name":"Python 3","language":"python","name":"python3"},"language_info":{"name":"python","version":"3.10.0"}},"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":4}
